03:06.646 --> 03:08.356
Hello?

03:08.731 --> 03:11.483
Hi. No, I'm fine.
I just stubbed my toe.

03:11.484 --> 03:15.154
Hang on one second, will you?
Honey, it's Hildy.

03:15.446 --> 03:17.115
I'll call her back.

03:17.365 --> 03:19.575
She's in the bathroom.

03:19.701 --> 03:21.577
She wants to know
what you're wearing.

03:22.412 --> 03:24.122
My black suit.

03:24.288 --> 03:26.707
She's gonna wear
her black dress.

03:26.708 --> 03:30.294
Well, it's gonna be business.
You know how those things are.

03:30.545 --> 03:33.088
Ellen, I don't want
you messing with
my make-up now,

03:33.089 --> 03:34.923
honey, okay?
I'm late.

03:34.924 --> 03:36.758
DAN: Is her red dress okay?

03:36.759 --> 03:37.844
BETH: It's perfect.

03:37.845 --> 03:42.639
Did you hear that?
You got it. Okay, darling,
see you later. Bye.

03:42.640 --> 03:44.142
Oh, man.

03:44.267 --> 03:45.600
BETH: I've told you
a million times

03:45.601 --> 03:48.562
not to play with
my lipstick, right?

03:48.563 --> 03:53.234
So when are you
gonna listen to me,
huh? Silly girl.

03:56.696 --> 03:58.864
Honey, where's my blue suit?

03:58.865 --> 04:00.742
It's on the back of the door.

04:02.452 --> 04:03.619
Oh!

04:05.079 --> 04:06.581
Oh, shit!

04:07.540 --> 04:08.915
Shit, shit, shit!

04:08.916 --> 04:10.208
[DOORBELL RINGING]

04:10.209 --> 04:12.128
Shit, shit, shit.

